Package: MIMIC3db
Title: Package for building, loading and referencing a SQLite version of the MIMIC-III v1.4 database on a local network
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "H. David",
           family = "Shea",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hdshea@comcast.net",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package provides a tightly bound set of routines to build a SQLite version of the 
    MIMIC-III v1.4 database on a local network.  The package has routines that then assist the user 
    with loading the MIMIC-III data into the local database.  The package also presents base routines 
    for accessing data from the database.
